Item: I tell the truth even when it’s hard.
I keep promises and follow through.
I act with kindness when people annoy me.
I choose what is right over what is easy.
I help people because I care, not to look good.
I forgive instead of holding grudges.
I stay humble when I succeed.
I check my motives before I act.
I pray and read Scripture regularly.
I honor God with my time and work.
I love my neighbor in practical ways.
I make changes when I learn God wants something different.
